dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents parks for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Parks_2017.gdb. [The Parks layer depicts Parks and Recreation Trails in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin. Parks are copied from the Parcel layer.]
